<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="night-and-day-day-and-night">night and day / day and night</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>日日夜夜；夜以继日：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was so diligent that he worked day and night.
他非常勤奋，夜以继日地工作。</p><footer>2008 湖南书面表达</footer></div></div>